Nodejs is written in C++, at the heart of the nodejs there is V8 engine.
V8 is Googleâ€™s open source high-performance JavaScript engine, written in C++ and used in Google Chrome and in Node.js, among others.

Download and install the latest versions from here:
    https://nodejs.org/en/

npmjs Probably just same to node as pypi is to python

npm Probably just same to node as pip is to python

"npm init" creates package.json which lists all the required packages by our code.
and can be used to install all the packages at a go.
(-y can be added for creating with default value)

Nodemon can be installed with npm and Nodemon is a great dev package that keeps track
of code changes in our application, and restarts the server for us when it detects them

